content: There are too many glitches, it freezes and the app crashes after 2 minutes of use ever since the new update. And please bring back the option of whether you want to separately quote retweet or just retweet a post. *Update: aside from the quote retweets, the same thing from last year is now happening again ever since the new update.

Twitter please fix this asap I can't receive any new notifications and it's only one at a time. I can't scroll down for old notifs when it's only that keeps appearing there. The problem would be resolved for a bit then it goes back to me not being able to reply to tweets and have had to resort to using the "Quote Tweet" tab to reply to tweets.
